    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and<strong> tomato paste </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>",
